data.description: A forever home -beautiful ranch with 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths in Portage Schools.  You'll love the living room with hardwood floors, gas fireplace, & dining area with built in shelving. The updated kitchen offers snack bar seating, granite counters & gas range. The primary has a walkthrough closet leading to a large spa like bath with soaking tub, two vanities & 6-8 person sauna! Basement has a living room & abundant storage. New 2023 radiant heat boiler & on-demand water heater! Imagine the possibilities in the HUGE 3 seasons room off the back of the oversized garage - perfect for entertaining, crafts & more! Fenced corner lot with convenient natural gas grill hookup. Centrally located & convenient to highway, shopping, dining & more!
